---
import BoxIcon from "./BoxIcon.astro";
// Testimonials section component
---

<section class="py-20 bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-4">
        The best way to manage fire protection systems. Period.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-background-card dark:bg-background-card-dark rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex">
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
          "With CAPCo, we've seen our project completion time drop nearly 30%. Having everything
          managed in one central place gives our team much more control and visibility into our fire
          protection projects."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm">KS</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark">
              Kevin Suchy
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-text-muted">Fire Protection Engineer</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-background-card dark:bg-background-card-dark rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex">
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
            <BoxIcon name="heart" size="sm" variant="solid" color="#f59e0b" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
          "CAPCo makes it incredibly easy to set up new projects; I can create 10 new ones a day if
          needed. This agility has allowed us to scale up to handle larger commercial projects."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-semibold text-sm">YV</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark">
              Yohai Vidergor
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-text-muted">VP of Operations</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-background-card dark:bg-background-card-dark rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex text-warning-400">
            <BoxIcon name="user" variant="solid" />
            <BoxIcon name="star" size="sm" variant="solid" />
            <BoxIcon name="star" size="sm" variant="solid" />
            <BoxIcon name="star" size="sm" variant="solid" />
            <BoxIcon name="star" size="sm" variant="solid" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-4">
          "CAPCo emerged as a better fit for our long-term goals, offering the kind of scalable
          environment and dedicated support we needed. The migration was streamlined and completed
          within a two-week sprint."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <span class="text-purple-600 font-semibold text-sm">JM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark">
              John Marriott
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-text-muted">
              Manager, Fire Safety Team
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why CAPCo Section -->
    <div class="bg-background-card dark:bg-background-card-dark rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-4">
          Why CAPCo?
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Reason 1 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
          >
            <BoxIcon name="zap" size="lg" color="#2563eb" />
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-2">
            Purpose-built to scale fire protection.
          </h4>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark text-sm">
            Other systems treat fire protection as an afterthought. Not CAPCo. We deliver 2x the
            performance and cut costs with smart automation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Reason 2 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
          >
            <BoxIcon name="bar-chart-alt-2" size="lg" color="#16a34a" />
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-2">
            Built-in compliance tracking. No extra tools required.
          </h4>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark text-sm">
            Other solutions force you to bolt on additional tools. CAPCo bakes in compliance
            tracking, inspection scheduling, and audit trails in one seamless interface.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Reason 3 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
          >
            <BoxIcon name="shield" size="lg" color="#9333ea" />
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary-dark mb-2">
            Enterprise security meets developer experience.
          </h4>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark text-sm">
            Secure, SOC 2 compliant, zero-trust architecture without sacrificing ease of use from
            project setup to final compliance certification.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
